{"lastModified":1773138622541,"uri":"c::7819198774::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Fiji, New Zealand, South Pacific, Australia\nHome Port: South Pacific\n\nAt 39.4 metres, 4A is a rare combination of design pedigree and modern performance. Built entirely from aluminium, her metallic silver hull and clean, sculpted lines turn heads in every harbour. Her fold-down balconies in the saloon and master suite bring the ocean into your living space, while her full-beam\naft deck beach club delivers a barefoot-to-water experience unlike any other. The sun deck, complete with bar,\ndaybeds, BBQ, and awning, is made for afternoons that melt into evenings. Five beautifully appointed ensuite cabins accommodate up to ten guests in complete comfort. And when it’s time for adventure, a full toy line-up awaits — from Seabobs and paddleboards to snorkelling gear and a secure, childfriendly netted pool.","blueprint":{"name":"4A","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e675b380-dbf1-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e6758c70-dbf1-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e6773a20-dbf1-11f0-b444-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e6753e50-dbf1-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e673b7b0-dbf1-11f0-b443-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e678c0c0-dbf1-11f0-b444-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e6773a21-dbf1-11f0-b444-61339ebdcb68/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfb28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::ass